{
  "stem": "18626.12",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 53.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because you had to have a guarantee that you bring to the United States that you can supply them with work.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my uncle was like almost like a one-man shop.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He had the same trade like me, woodturning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the pool cues.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He used to make the billiards sticks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So it took a long time till I got my papers to come to the United States.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my uncle was told that I'm going to leave Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And before I left Germany, a CIA man came to my home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was living there no more at the villa [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I was living in a private room.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The villa [INAUDIBLE] was given away then already to the family.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Little by little, you know, the Germans start to get back, you understand.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So a CIA man came with a dog and a Jeep.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I lived in a German house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If the German would said one word about me that I'm not a good man, they wouldn't let me into the United States.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I felt bad about that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That part, I felt bad, that CIA was questioning a German.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was not the SS man, but he was still a German and he was a [? sympatico ?] and for Hitler in the good days.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Of what did you hear about Moses?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Does he behave good?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Is he a honest man?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So luckily, the people, these Germans liked me, so they tell a good opinion on me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So the German [INAUDIBLE] came with a typewriter right in the room and he wrote everything.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they had a German dog with them in the Jeep.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they wrote up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He says, and he gave me a knock on the shoulder, I think we'll see in America.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
